fields.name: Healthy Bolognese
fields.description: This Healthy Bolognese is our signature sample meal. We combine lean pork mince with fennel and cherry tomatoes to get a low-fat low-calorie meal ready to eat with minimal cooking effort.

fields.name: Salmon Pasta
fields.description: Looking to try something healthy and delicious at the same time as keeping the calories down? Why not try out Salmon pasta. We only use the best ingredients with healthy and nutritious options chosen at every preparation step.

fields.name: Chicken Kiev
fields.description: This tasty dish brings you flavour while keeping the calories down. Our chicken kiev only uses 3 ingredients, and with only being 220kcal it is the perfect way to get some great protein whilst keeping the calories down.

fields.name: Spicy Chicken & Avocado Wrap
fields.description: Looking for something spicy that is healthy at the same time? Why not give our spicy chicken avocado wraps a go. With only 403 calories and 23g of protein, these are perfect for the gym goer in a hurry.

fields.name: Vegan Burger
fields.description: Cautious about what way your food is prepared? Well we have you covered! With out vegan burger we guarantee that we fully exclude any animal products while keeping a nutritious and balanced meal.
